<blockquote>
<p>
:snowflake: Add <b>Nix support</b> for <b>external dependencies (depexts)</=
b> by adding support for stateless package managers (<a href=3D"https://git=
hub.com/ocaml/opam/issues/5982">#5982</a>). <i>Thanks to <a href=3D"https:/=
